<style>
<% if @page.title == 'Izon' %>
    #l2-bike {background-image:url(/assets/bike-bg-izon.jpg);}
  <% elsif @page.title == 'Skylon' %>
    #l2-bike {background-image:url(/assets/bike-bg-skylon.jpg);}
  <% else %>
    #l2-bike {background-image:url(/assets/bike-bg-fluidity.jpg);}
<% end %>
</style>



<section class="show" id="l2-bike">
  <div class="container">
    <%#= render '/refinery/content_page' %>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-8" id="bike-img">
        <%= image_tag 'Izon-AKTIV-red-bike.png', class: 'img-responsive1' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4" id="bike-main-txt">
        <%= image_tag 'IZON-LOGO-black.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
        
          <h3>Reactive</h3>
          <h3>Polyvalence</h3>
          <h3>Agility</h3>
        
        <p class="lead">
          IZON is the ideal all around bike – climbing or descending those long switchbacks to attacking around a corner in a criterium – the intuitiveness of the IZON will surprise you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="aktiv-choice">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
        <%= image_tag 'Izon-red-frame.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-6">
        <%= image_tag 'Izon-AKTIV-red-frame.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">

    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-1 col-md-4 col-md-offset-1 col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-1">
        <h1 class="text-center">Smooth...</h1>
        <p>Your roads are smooth and a IZON with a 'traditional' fork and a normal seatpost will provide you all day racing and riding comfort.</p>
        <p>Like every TIME frame, it's 100% MADE IN FRANCE and uses RTM technology to deliver a strong frame that's a perfect balance of responsiveness and comfort.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-2 text-center" id="or">
        <h1>or</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4">
        <h1 class="text-center">...Smoother</h1>
        <p>Not all roads are perfect. And in some places, no roads are perfect. The IZON with an AKTIV fork paves the way for you, reducing micro-vibrations (as much as 30%) to your body using tuned-mass damper technology.</p>

        <p>The AKTIV frames also employ the Translink integrated seatmast giving you additional comfort and reducing weight.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

